{"title":"访友——小城三部曲","authors":["木斧"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":8,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"访友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——小城三部曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木斧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、风筝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆是我手中长长的线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放飞天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那风华正茂的少年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞姿蹁跹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怨你生来太轻薄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经不住风的赞扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我手中的线断了，听说你落在一座小城中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、小城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小城如你的相貌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不涂脂抹粉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不炫耀艳丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有旅游者的朝拜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有进香人的祝愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你初坠小城可不是这个样儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小城把你磨纯朴了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小城当年也不是这个模样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪来满城琅琅的读书声？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今你是小城的大名人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃李遍天下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候我觉得小城太大了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如你一间读书的小屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、小屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白昼和黑夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在小屋内失去颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读书读白了头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人影在粉墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画出了弯曲的弓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月在弓上急驰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把时光拉成一条线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年龄，被遗弃在门外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功名与富贵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已逃之夭夭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煮酒论英雄，话雨纷纷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落了一夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜湿了窗棂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推开小屋大吃一惊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个世纪流逝了"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}